Sniper


Sniper hears Prowl's Transmision. Everyone seated. Okay. "Sniper to 
Striker, Make sure everyone stays in the war room except prowl, your 
in command in there." Sniper runs toward the outside, where all the 
explosins are. He pulls out his gun not noticing Prowl right infront 
of him. He runs into Prowl, Flying about 20 feet he hits the wall. He 
gets up, "I came to help you." Sniper rubs his head finding that
there 
is a dent in it. "Lets go."
